BRANDON HERRING: So Google
Pay gives users one place

00:03:26.850 --> 00:03:29.760
to easily manage all
their payment information.

00:03:29.760 --> 00:03:32.580
From seeing the cards
and keeping sure

00:03:32.580 --> 00:03:34.620
