00:03:34.620 --> 00:03:36.780
transactions, Google
Pay is giving users

00:03:36.780 --> 00:03:39.220
a flexible and comprehensive
digital wallet.

00:03:43.860 --> 00:03:46.510
And users, they can leverage
this account information

00:03:46.510 --> 00:03:52.420
to speed through checkout, in
apps, online, and in-store.

00:03:52.420 --> 00:03:55.930
The app already has more
than 100 million installs,

00:03:55.930 --> 00:03:58.040
