00:04:26.040 --> 00:04:29.160
And users, with a payment method
linked to their Google account,

00:04:29.160 --> 00:04:34.170
can checkout instantly anywhere
they see the Google Pay button.

00:04:34.170 --> 00:04:36.450
And because hundreds of
millions of payment methods

00:04:36.450 --> 00:04:38.460
