With Google Pay,
users are instantly

00:04:48.800 --> 00:04:52.190
ready to check out the first
time they visit an app or site

00:04:52.190 --> 00:04:54.149
or even in a guest
check out flow.

00:04:54.149 --> 00:04:55.940
They no longer need to
