out quickly and easily.

00:05:03.530 --> 00:05:06.780
And with less friction, the
user experience has improved,

00:05:06.780 --> 00:05:09.660
users are happier, and
transactions increase.

00:05:09.660 --> 00:05:11.490
And we're seeing this
already validated

00:05:11.490 --> 00:05:13.740
with a lot of our partners.

