00:05:21.130 --> 00:05:24.070
and Airbnb has seen their
traction volume jump

00:05:24.070 --> 00:05:27.514
11 times since implementing the
latest version of Google Pay.

00:05:27.514 --> 00:05:29.680
And Jenny is going to tell
us a little bit about how

00:05:29.680 --> 00:05:30.760
we got there.

